That's why we've developed a suite of AI solutions that can help you automate these tasks so you can focus on more important things. Our platform brings together the power of blockchain and AI to provide you with a seamless and efficient experience.Our AI products: AI Editor | AI Creator | Earn with AI (Soon) | AI Powered Launchpad (Soon)Bounty General Details1. Bounty will be manage via Zealy App  GPTCash Zealy Quest Board 2. Bounty Stakes will be points based via Zealy to automate stakes calculation and faster token rewards distribution3. Bitcointalk account is not a requirement4. GPTCash Zealy Campaign will run from April 27 to May 14, 2023.5. Rewards distribution will be sent 30 days after the campaign.Available Quest/Bounty1.
